data.description: This home's unique layout perfectly accommodates all of your needs. It features a newly renovated kitchen, updated flooring, cathedral ceilings, original brick accent walls, and an oversized primary bedroom. Enjoy the fully fenced backyard with a deck that allows for all kinds of social events! Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac. Minutes from Lynnhaven Mall and Mt. Trashmore Park. Don't miss the chance to make this residence your own – schedule a viewing today!
